GNS3 VM Setup/Configuration

VM Setup/Configuration - Portnox

1.) Deploy OVA/Image from GNS3 Website (VMware ESXi)
2.) Configure the Hardware:
     Memory: 24 GB
     Processors: 4 (2 sockets, 2 cores) [host]
     BIOS, Display, Machine: Default
     Networks: Virtio
3.) Configure Network Hardware as following
     net0 - GNS3 Management VLAN (254)
     net1 - Outside Internet GNS3 VLAN (150)
     net2 - Inside Private GNS3 VLAN (151)
4.) Configure /etc/netplan/90_gns3vm_static_netcfg.yaml
     eth0:
        dhcp4: no
        addresses
        - 10.0.254.1/24
        gateway4: 10.0.254.254
        nameservers:
          addresses: [8.8.8.8, 8.8.4.4]

     eth1:
        dhcp4: yes
     eth2:
        dhcp4: yes

5.) Test in Web or Client each Interface
      eth0 = eth0
      eth1 = eth1
      eth2 = eth2
